  32:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****                      ##### How to use this driver #####
  33:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****   ==============================================================================
  34:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****   [..]
  35:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****     *** Channel initialization ***
  36:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****     ==============================
  37:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****     [..]
  38:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****       (#) User has first to initialize channels (before filters initialization).
  39:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****       (#) As prerequisite, fill in the HAL_DFSDM_ChannelMspInit() :
  40:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****         (++) Enable DFSDMz clock interface with __HAL_RCC_DFSDMz_CLK_ENABLE().
  41:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****         (++) Enable the clocks for the DFSDMz GPIOS with __HAL_RCC_GPIOx_CLK_ENABLE().
  42:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****         (++) Configure these DFSDMz pins in alternate mode using HAL_GPIO_Init().
  43:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****         (++) If interrupt mode is used, enable and configure DFSDMz_FLT0 global
  44:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****             interrupt with HAL_NVIC_SetPriority() and HAL_NVIC_EnableIRQ().
  45:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****       (#) Configure the output clock, input, serial interface, analog watchdog,
  46:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           offset and data right bit shift parameters for this channel using the
  47:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           HAL_DFSDM_ChannelInit() function.
  48:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c **** 
  49:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****     *** Channel clock absence detector ***
  50:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****     ======================================
  51:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****     [..]
  52:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****       (#) Start clock absence detector using HAL_DFSDM_ChannelCkabStart() or
  53:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           HAL_DFSDM_ChannelCkabStart_IT().
  54:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****       (#) In polling mode, use HAL_DFSDM_ChannelPollForCkab() to detect the clock
  55:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           absence.
  56:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****       (#) In interrupt mode, HAL_DFSDM_ChannelCkabCallback() will be called if
  57:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           clock absence is detected.
  58:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****       (#) Stop clock absence detector using HAL_DFSDM_ChannelCkabStop() or
  59:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           HAL_DFSDM_ChannelCkabStop_IT().
  60:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****       (#) Please note that the same mode (polling or interrupt) has to be used
  61:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           for all channels because the channels are sharing the same interrupt.
  62:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****       (#) Please note also that in interrupt mode, if clock absence detector is
  63:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           stopped for one channel, interrupt will be disabled for all channels.
  64:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c **** 
  65:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****     *** Channel short circuit detector ***
  66:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****     ======================================
  67:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****     [..]
  68:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****       (#) Start short circuit detector using HAL_DFSDM_ChannelScdStart() or
  69:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           or HAL_DFSDM_ChannelScdStart_IT().
  70:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****       (#) In polling mode, use HAL_DFSDM_ChannelPollForScd() to detect short
  71:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           circuit.
  72:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****       (#) In interrupt mode, HAL_DFSDM_ChannelScdCallback() will be called if
  73:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           short circuit is detected.
  74:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****       (#) Stop short circuit detector using HAL_DFSDM_ChannelScdStop() or
  75:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           or HAL_DFSDM_ChannelScdStop_IT().
  76:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****       (#) Please note that the same mode (polling or interrupt) has to be used
  77:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           for all channels because the channels are sharing the same interrupt.
  78:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****       (#) Please note also that in interrupt mode, if short circuit detector is
  79:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           stopped for one channel, interrupt will be disabled for all channels.
  80:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c **** 
  81:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****     *** Channel analog watchdog value ***
  82:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****     =====================================
  83:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****     [..]
  84:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****       (#) Get analog watchdog filter value of a channel using
  85:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           HAL_DFSDM_ChannelGetAwdValue().
