  96:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****       (#) As prerequisite, fill in the HAL_DFSDM_FilterMspInit() :
  97:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****         (++) If interrupt mode is used , enable and configure DFSDMz_FLTx global
  98:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****             interrupt with HAL_NVIC_SetPriority() and HAL_NVIC_EnableIRQ().
  99:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****             Please note that DFSDMz_FLT0 global interrupt could be already
 100:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****             enabled if interrupt is used for channel.
 101:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****         (++) If DMA mode is used, configure DMA with HAL_DMA_Init() and link it
 102:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****             with DFSDMz filter handle using __HAL_LINKDMA().
 103:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****       (#) Configure the regular conversion, injected conversion and filter
 104:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           parameters for this filter using the HAL_DFSDM_FilterInit() function.
