 106:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****     *** Filter regular channel conversion ***
 107:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****     =========================================
 108:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****     [..]
 109:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****       (#) Select regular channel and enable/disable continuous mode using
 110:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           HAL_DFSDM_FilterConfigRegChannel().
 111:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****       (#) Start regular conversion using HAL_DFSDM_FilterRegularStart(),
 112:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           HAL_DFSDM_FilterRegularStart_IT(), HAL_DFSDM_FilterRegularStart_DMA() or
 113:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           HAL_DFSDM_FilterRegularMsbStart_DMA().
 114:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****       (#) In polling mode, use HAL_DFSDM_FilterPollForRegConversion() to detect
 115:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           the end of regular conversion.
 116:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****       (#) In interrupt mode, HAL_DFSDM_FilterRegConvCpltCallback() will be called
 117:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           at the end of regular conversion.
 118:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****       (#) Get value of regular conversion and corresponding channel using
 119:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           HAL_DFSDM_FilterGetRegularValue().
 120:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****       (#) In DMA mode, HAL_DFSDM_FilterRegConvHalfCpltCallback() and
 121:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           HAL_DFSDM_FilterRegConvCpltCallback() will be called respectively at the
 122:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           half transfer and at the transfer complete. Please note that
 123:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           HAL_DFSDM_FilterRegConvHalfCpltCallback() will be called only in DMA
 124:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           circular mode.
 125:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****       (#) Stop regular conversion using HAL_DFSDM_FilterRegularStop(),
 126:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_hal_dfsdm.c ****           HAL_DFSDM_FilterRegularStop_IT() or HAL_DFSDM_FilterRegularStop_DMA().
